1.1 Executive Summary
The AI Business Operating System (AIBOS) is a multi-tenant, production-grade automation platform that orchestrates five specialized AI agents (CFO, Marketing, Sales, Operations, CEO) to reduce manual work for seed-stage startups by 80% while maintaining military-grade security and compliance.
Target Customers: Seed-stage founders ($1M–$10M raised), 0–50 team members

Total Addressable Market (TAM): $2B (100,000 startups × $20K/year ARPU)

Unit Economics: CAC $500, LTV $100K+ (12-year retention), Gross Margin 85%

1.2 Core System Objectives:
PRIMARY_OBJECTIVES:
  1. Orchestrate 5 specialized AI agents without latency (p95 < 200ms)
  2. Execute 1000+ automated tasks daily with 99.5% reliability
  3. Maintain complete data isolation per customer (zero cross-tenant data leaks)
  4. Provide real-time decision-making dashboard for founders
  5. Maintain 7-year immutable audit trail for compliance
  6. Scale from MVP (5 customers) to 1000 customers without architectural changes

